short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Play Sudoku on your new browser tab

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Play the most popular puzzle game of all time right from your new browser tab. SudokuNewTab features unlimited games in three different skill levels. 

This extension also features a web search powered by Bing. 

Privacy policy: https://sudokutab.com/privacy-policy/
Terms of use:  https://sudokutab.com/terms-of-service/
Contact us: https://sudokutab.com/contact
Uninstall info: https://sudokutab.com/uninstall/
About us: https://sudokutab.com/about-us/

Permissions requested by this extension:

Storage: Stores session data related to the active sudoku game being played.
